{"pageProps":{"article":{"id":"63bfde2fec","title":"周恩来对开封武斗问题的指示","origin":"","is_range_date":false,"dates":[{"id":"474316c10f","index":0,"year":1967,"month":9,"day":5,"articleId":"63bfde2fec","article":{}}],"tags":[{"name":"指示","id":"2d13338754","type":"文稿类型"},{"name":"暴力和武斗","id":"3bff1d2fc6","type":"主题"},{"name":"周恩来","id":"523bb79e8f","type":"人物"},{"name":"周总理","id":"838b5f2c9d","type":"人物"},{"name":"关键人物文稿","id":"c20d333791","type":"文稿大类"}],"aliases":[],"publications":[{"id":"wenku","name":"中国文化大革命文库（第一版）","internal":false,"official":false,"type":"db","author":"宋永毅","files":"","articles":[],"comments":[],"contents":[],"pages":[]}],"authors":[]},"publication_details":{"wenku":{"comments":[],"contents":[{"id":"074048fe55","type":"title","text":"周恩来对开封武斗问题的指示","index":0,"publicationId":"wenku","articleId":"63bfde2fec","publication":{},"article":{}},{"id":"bb10046ba1","type":"paragraph","text":"九月四日晚九时以后，老保先后对我仪表、空分、阀门、拖电等厂进行骚扰袭击，叫喊要消灭六零九三和造反派，并冲击我高压阀门厂，使用黄色炸药。一军杨政委和杜副军长先后向周总理反映了这一情况。九月五日上午八时四十五分，河南省军区党委办公室秘书组周成继同志来电：总理很关心开封问题。总理指示我们向老保明确指出：","index":1,"publicationId":"wenku","articleId":"63bfde2fec","publication":{},"article":{}},{"id":"7da32e53f8","type":"paragraph","text":"“必须立即停止进攻，放下武器，得到保护。消灭造反派和驻军是反革命行动。”","index":2,"publicationId":"wenku","articleId":"63bfde2fec","publication":{},"article":{}}],"page":{"start":0,"end":0}}}},"__N_SSG":true}